title: Windy City Rehab: Alison's Dream Home
overview: Windy City Rehab: Alison's Dream Home will spotlight the riskiest and most personal project ever for popular designer and home renovation expert Alison Victoria. Now she is ready to share more of her journey as she transforms her current Chicago office—a 6,250-square foot warehouse built in 1930—into her very own "live-work" dream home.
